The purpose of this purchase was to offer its customers more services and value-added, with the opportunity to gain access to a huge international market.
This review and purchase service is exclusively addressed to professionals such as insurance companies, experts, car rental companies, workshops, scrap shops and car dealers who need to be registered prior to their activities.
This platform was founded in 1996 in Germany and manages more than 650,000 operations across Europe, 500,000 of which alone in Germany.
Their main markets are Spain, Greece, Poland and Turkey.
Today, the website has more than 1,500 registered sellers and 4,000 experts.
Every day 3,000 ads are managed and 100 new ads are added to the Spanish market every day.
